": false, \"api_host\": \"https://readthedocs.org\", \"build_date\": \"2021-04-24T21:21:14Z\", \"builder\": \"sphinx\", \"canonical_url\": null, \"commit\": \"64284c00\", \"docroot\": \"/docs/\", \"features\": {\"docsearch_disabled\": false}, \"global_analytics_code\": \"UA-17997319-1\", \"language\": \"en\", \"page\": \"index\", \"programming_language\": \"py\", \"project\": \"pytest-incremental\", \"proxied_api_host\": \"/_\", \"source_suffix\": \".rst\", \"subprojects\": {}, \"theme\": \"sphinxdoc\", \"user_analytics_code\": \"\", \"version\": \"latest\"}</script><!--Using this variable directly instead of using `JSON.parse` is deprecated.The READTHEDOCS_DATA global variable will be removed in the future.--><script type=\"text/javascript\">READTHEDOCS_DATA = JSON.parse(document.getElementById('READTHEDOCS_DATA').innerHTML);</script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://assets.readthedocs.org/static/javascript/readthedocs-analytics.js\" async=\"async\"></script><!-- end RTD <extrahead> --></head><body>    <div class=\"related\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"related navigation\">      <h3>Navigation</h3>      <ul>        <li class=\"right\" style=\"margin-right: 10px\">          <a href=\"genindex.html\" title=\"General Index\"             accesskey=\"I\">index</a></li>        <li class=\"right\" >          <a href=\"runner.html\" title=\"Test Runners\"             accesskey=\"N\">next</a> |</li>        <li class=\"right\" >          <a href=\"contents.html\" title=\"pytest-incremental documentation\"             accesskey=\"P\">previous</a> |</li>        <li class=\"nav-item nav-item-0\"><a href=\"contents.html\">pytest-incremental 0.5 documentation</a> &#187;</li>       </ul>    </div>      <div class=\"sphinxsidebar\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"main navigation\">        <div class=\"sphinxsidebarwrapper\">  <h3><a href=\"contents.html\">Table of Contents</a></h3>  <ul><li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">pytest-incremental: py.test plugin - incremental test runner</a><ul><li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#install\">Install</a></li><li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#usage\">Usage</a><ul><li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#watched-packages\">watched packages</a></li><li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#dependencies\">dependencies</a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>  <h4>Previous topic</h4>  <p class=\"topless\"><a href=\"contents.html\"                        title=\"previous chapter\">pytest-incremental documentation</a></p>  <h4>Next topic</h4>  <p class=\"topless\"><a href=\"runner.html\"                        title=\"next chapter\">Test Runners</a></p>  <div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"source link\">    <h3>This Page</h3>    <ul class=\"this-page-menu\">      <li><a href=\"_sources/index.rst.txt\"            rel=\"nofollow\">Show Source</a></li>    </ul>   </div><div id=\"searchbox\" style=\"display: none\" role=\"search\">  <h3>Quick search</h3>    <div class=\"searchformwrapper\">    <form class=\"search\" action=\"search.html\" method=\"get\">      <input type=\"text\" name=\"q\" />      <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Go\" />      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"check_keywords\" value=\"yes\" />      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"area\" value=\"default\" />    </form>    </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\">$('#searchbox').show(0);</script>        </div>      </div>    <div class=\"document\">      <div class=\"documentwrapper\">        <div class=\"bodywrapper\">          <div class=\"body\" role=\"main\">              <div class=\"section\" id=\"pytest-incremental-py-test-plugin-incremental-test-runner\"><h1>pytest-incremental: py.test plugin - incremental test runner<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#pytest-incremental-py-test-plugin-incremental-test-runner\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1><dl class=\"docutils\"><dt>Github:</dt><dd><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-incremental\">https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-incremental</a></dd><dt>PyPI:</dt><dd><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pytest-incremental\">https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pytest-incremental</a></dd></dl><p><cite>pytest-incremental</cite> is a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://pytest.org/\">py.test</a> plug-in.It analyses your project structure and file modifications between test-runsto modify the order tests are executed and de-select tests.This allows a much faster feedback for interactive test execution.</p><p>Check the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"runner.html#motivation\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">documentation</span></a> for more details.</p><p>Note that <em>py.test</em> has support to run standard unittest\u2019s and nose\u2019s tests.So even if you don\u2019t use <em>py.test</em> as a test framework you might be able touse it as a test runner.</p><div class=\"section\" id=\"install\"><h2>Install<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#install\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2><p>pytest-incremental is tested on python 3.6-3.9, pytest 6.x.</p><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">pip</span> <span class=\"pre\">install</span> <span class=\"pre\">pytest-incremental</span></code></p></div><div class=\"section\" id=\"usage\"><h2>Usage<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usage\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2><p>Just pass the parameter <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">--inc</span></code> when calling from the command line:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc</pre></div></div><p>You can also enable it by default adding the followingline to your <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">pytest.ini</span></code>:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">pytest</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"n\">addopts</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">inc</span></pre></div></div><div class=\"section\" id=\"watched-packages\"><h3>watched packages<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#watched-packages\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3><p>By default all modules from within your <em>CWD</em> will be counted as dependenciesif imported. In order to limit or extend the watched folders you must usethe parameter <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">--inc-path</span></code></p><p>This can be used in case you want to watch for changes in modules that arein another project.For example if you are testing <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">my_lib</span></code> and want to check for changesin dependencies from your <cite>py3rd</cite> package:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc --inc-path my_lib --inc-path ../py3rd-trunk/py3rd</pre></div></div></div><div class=\"section\" id=\"dependencies\"><h3>dependencies<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#dependencies\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3><p>You can check what are the actual dependencies detected by running the command:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc-deps</pre></div></div><p>for better visualization you can create a graph file in \u201cdot\u201d format(see <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://www.graphviz.org/\">graphviz</a> ):</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc-graph</pre></div></div><p>To generate an image:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc-graph-image</pre></div></div><p>You can also check what are the outdated tests without executing them:</p><div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>$ py.test --inc-outdated</pre></div></div></div></div></div>          </div>        </div>      </div>      <div class=\"clearer\"></div>    </div>    <div class=\"related\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"related navigation\">      <h3>Navigation</h3>      <ul>        <li class=\"right\" style=\"margin-right: 10px\">          <a href=\"genindex.html\" title=\"General Index\"             >index</a></li>        <li class=\"right\" >          <a href=\"runner.html\" title=\"Test Runners\"             >next</a> |</li>        <li class=\"right\" >          <a href=\"contents.html\" title=\"pytest-incremental documentation\"             >previous</a> |</li>        <li class=\"nav-item nav-item-0\"><a href=\"contents.html\">pytest-incremental 0.5 documentation</a> &#187;</li>       </ul>    </div>    <div class=\"footer\" role=\"contentinfo\">        &#169; Copyright 2018, schettino72.      Created using <a href=\"http://sphinx-doc.org/\">Sphinx</a> 1.8.5.    </div>  </body></html>",
